<div type="abstract"><head>Rat an Konrad von Aufseß</head><p>Der Rat bittet für Hans und H. Paudler von Buckenhofen, Armmänner von St. Sebald zu Nürnberg, um Einhaltung der mit Peter Volckamer und Stefan Koler, Ratsherrn und Bürger zu Nürnberg, vereinbarten Fristverlängerung der bischöflichen Steuerforderungen (vgl. Nr. 2838).</p>
</div>
<!--This div could possibly contain the analytic portion of the edition.-->
<div type="linguisticAnalysis"><ab><w join="" lemma="" msd="" part="" pos=""><fLib><f name=" "/></fLib></w></ab></div>
</front>
<body><div type="diplomatic"><pb facs="#facs_401" id="199v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee"><del rend="crossout"><ab facs="#facs_401_r1l24"><expan>eide<ex>m</ex></expan> </ab>
</del></div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<del rend="crossout"><ab facs="#facs_401_r1l25">Vns hat
                                    <expan>fürg<ex>elegt</ex></expan> hans Ryeter
                                    <expan>pfleg<ex>er</ex></expan> des
                                <expan>Gotſh<ex>aus</ex></expan> cʒu ſant </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_401_r1l26">Sebolt / vvie Jm <expan>han<ex>n</ex>s</expan>
                            vnd <expan cert="unknown">h</expan>  die pawdler von
                                    <expan>puke<ex>n</ex>hofe<ex>n</ex></expan>
</ab>
<ab facs="#facs_401_r1l27">
<del rend="strikethrough">fürbraht </del>
<expan>deſſ<ex>elben</ex></expan>
<expan>Gocʒh<ex>aus</ex></expan> Armman <expan>fürbr<ex>aht</ex></expan>
<expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> etc vt <expan>ſup<ex>ra</ex></expan>
</ab>
</del>
</div>
</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_401" id="199v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab><del rend="crossout"><expan>Eide<ex>m</ex></expan></del></ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab><del rend="crossout">Uns hat <expan>fürg<ex>elegt</ex></expan> Hans Ryeter,
                                    <expan>pfleg<ex>er</ex></expan> des
                                <expan>gotsh<ex>aus</ex></expan> czu sant Sebolt, wie im
                                    <expan>Han<ex>n</ex>s</expan> und <expan cert="unknown">H.</expan>, die Pawdler von
                                <expan>Puke<ex>n</ex>hofe<ex>n</ex></expan>,
                                    <expan>dess<ex>elben</ex></expan>
<expan>goczh<ex>aus</ex></expan> armman,
                                <expan>fürbr<ex>aht</ex></expan>
<expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> etc. ut
                            <expan>sup<ex>ra</ex></expan>.</del></ab>
</div>
